List Of Frequently Asked Questions

What is gettrippy shop?

Gettrippy shop is the place to buy & sell illegal goods and services from guaranteed suppliers in the world’s online 24/7 market! Top quality, cheap and free shipping on many products. All transactions are secured anonymously to stakeholders.

What is user privacy?

We do not share your activity with any third party. What happens on our servers, is still on our servers. All personal information relating to privacy is fully encrypted at 100% and periodically deleted.

What are the return policies?

The return policies for your order depend on your order vendor, read and find out their return policy information before making an order for a specific product. Drugon Shop is just where the intermediate trades make transactions. We only deal with complaints if they happen.

What are Cloned ATM Credit Card Pin?

  •   Cloning, also called skimming, is the copying of credit or debit card info to a new card.
  • The card information is stolen at the credit card terminal using software or electronic device and copied onto a new card.
  • Swiping the credit card through the device copies the information held on the magnetic strip into memory. That information can subsequently be copied to a counterfeit card, complete with security holograms.
  • Any type of bank card that has a magnetic stripe can be cloned. This includes credit cards, debit cards and normal ATM cards.
  • Chip cards, or EMV cards, were created to prevent cloning.
  • This cloned card can then be used to make purchases at point of sale devices and (where the customer’s personal identification number [PIN] has also been obtained) to make withdrawals from Automated teller machines (ATM)

what are shipper & dropper?

Shipper is the person who made the order through the online store. They are more experienced in credit card fraud, they only perform actions on the computer, the orders will be sent to the Dropper address.

Dropper is the recipient that helps shipper, they may be in common country or in another country. Why need dropper? Some shop don’t accept shipping to shipper country should need droppers. Dropper can receive calls or related confirmation from the store owner for shipper or make shipping name, for example shipper use the card from the USA, the address received also from the USA it seems valid rather than the delivery address in India

What are Tor?

Tor “The Onion Router” is a free and open source Browser that is located on the Quantum core of Firefox browser. Tor is a computer software that removes traces and hides the IP address of the Internet access machine when sending or receiving information over the Internet, implementing an onion-based routing protocol.

How to buy Bitcoin & other Crypto?

There are several ways you can buy bitcoin including:

  • Use Bitcoin exchange
  • Browse a P2P Directory
  • Use Bitcoin ATM

For more specific information, please visit: bitcoin.org/en/buy

We think you’ll also like:

  1. Blockchain : Blockchain Explorer & Wallet
  2. Coinbase : Buy & Sell Bitcoin, Ethereum, and more
  3. LocalBitcoins : Fastest and easiest way to buy and sell bitcoins
  4. Coinmama : Buy and Sell Cryptocurrency Online
  5. CEX.IO : Bitcoin Exchange | Bitcoin Trading
  6. Gemini : The Regulated Cryptocurrency Exchange
  7. Bitcoin.com : Buy BTC & BCH

What are shipping options?

We are supporting two main shipping methods, shipping digital products, and transporting physical products.
We encourage vendors to make free shipping options for orders, but if the vendors need to calculate their losses for the order, they can count it in the total price of the product.

What are the international taxes,duties,etc that a have to pay?

All transactions at DRAGON store are completely tax-free at 0% for customers to make trades.
Taxes for providers are at less than €150 for a month.

When will I receive an order?

You will receive an order usually as soon as your order is placed and the payment has been successfully executed. Vendors will update their order information and make shipping orders for you. Time lag is no more than 3 days.

What I do if I never receive the order?

The first is you don’t worry and patiently wait for your provider to answer your order. If your order is over time for shipping, contact our Customer care team to work with your provider and ask them to compensate/ or refund for your order.

What I do if i received a defective order?

Let’s talk to your provider directly to request a compensation contract for your order. If you have difficulties in claiming a defective product, please contact our customer service immediately to resolve your complaint.

How do I change the order I,ve placed?

If your order status is still being processed, immediately contact our customer service to cancel your order and receive a refund to your account. But if your order has been shipped, we are unable to change the status of your order.

What are you located?

Dragon currently exists only on the NET and the administrators are currently living and moving continuously around the world. We don’t use the residence rules of world rulers now, we have our own rules of residence!!
